OL,3,CPolice end search of woodland
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of firearm
OL,6,FA search of a wooded area in
OL,7,FSouthampton, following the discovery
OL,8,Fof a firearm, has ended.
OL,10,FHampshire Police was called to
OL,11,Fwoodland near to Wadhurst Gardens in
OL,12,FSholing on Tuesday 7 April, after two
OL,13,Fboys found a weapon in the area.
OL,15,FThe firearm was accidentally
OL,16,Fdischarged and a boy aged 11 was
OL,17,Ftreated for a graze to his head.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
