PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776096667
OL,3,CPolice end search of woodland
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of firearm
OL,6,FOn Sunday, officers ended their
OL,7,Fsearches and fully reopened the area.
OL,8,FInvestigations into how the weapon
OL,9,Fended up in the area are ongoing.
OL,11,FIn a statement, a spokesperson from
OL,12,FHampshire Police said: "On Tuesday
OL,13,Fevening (7 April), we began an
OL,14,Finvestigation after a firearm was
OL,15,Ffound by two boys in the woodland, who
OL,16,Fbelieved it was a BB gun.
OL,18,F"Having taken it home, the firearm was
OL,19,Fmistakenly discharged and grazed the
OL,20,Fhead of one of the boys.
OL,26,@tD@XOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
