PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776096667
OL,3,CPolice end search of woodland
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of firearm
OL,6,F"Since that time, we have remained at
OL,7,Fthe location where it was found,
OL,8,Fcarrying out an investigation and
OL,9,Fconducting enquiries.
OL,11,F"We want to thank local residents and
OL,12,Fpeople who regularly use the woodland
OL,13,Ffor their patience and understanding
OL,14,Fwhile this work has been conducted, we
OL,15,Frealise the disruption this has caused
OL,16,Fpeople but has been vitally important.
OL,18,F"Our investigation remains ongoing at
OL,19,Fthis time in relation to the firearm
OL,20,Frecovered, and when we have further
OL,21,Fupdates we can provide we will do so."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@fO]
